	<TextInfo>
		<Text Type="Business Summary" lastModified="2015-06-29T04:00:32">Costain Group PLC is a United Kingdom-based engineering solutions provider. The Company offers consulting, project delivery and operations and maintenance services. The Company operates through two segments: Natural Resources and Infrastructure. The Infrastructure segment operates in the highways, rail and power sectors. The Company delivers asset life-cycle solutions across the entire railway. It provides highways services and delivers technology-led solutions. In Power, it offers energy infrastructure. The Natural Resources segment delivers engineering solutions in water, nuclear, and oil andgas sectors. It provides engineering solutions to the United Kingdom water utility companies across the asset life-cycle. It creates facilities to manage nuclear waste safely. It provides life-cycle engineering services in the development, design, delivery and maintenance of oil and gas infrastructure. The Company also has land development operations in Spain.</Text>
		<Text Type="Financial Summary" lastModified="2015-08-21T08:11:59">BRIEF: For the six months ended 30 June 2015, Costain Group PLC revenues increased 19% to L601.5M. Net income increased 67% to L8.5M. Revenues reflect Infrastructure segment increase of 32% to L464M. Net income benefited from Infrastructure segment income increase of 42% to L22.8M, Central Costs segment loss decrease of 3% to L3M. Dividend per share increased from L0.03 to L0.04.</Text>
	</TextInfo>
